OL,6,FA cleaner has been jailed after using
OL,7,Fhis phone to spy on a woman showering
OL,8,Fat a gym.
OL,10,FLee Drury, 35, hid his device in the
OL,11,Fceiling of the gym in Tonbridge, Kent
OL,12,Fin June 2023.
OL,14,FThe victim noticed a dislodged ceiling
OL,15,Ftile before discovering the phone.
OL,17,FShe took photos of the ceiling and
OL,18,Falerted a manager.
