OL,6,FDrury, who had only been working at
OL,7,Fthe gym for a few months, was
OL,8,Fchallenged but when his phone was
OL,9,Fchecked no images were found.
OL,11,FDrury was arrested and a full forensic
OL,12,Fdownload of the phone showed he had
OL,13,Faccessed a camera app at the same time
OL,14,Fthe victim had been in the showers.
OL,16,FOfficers also recovered an illegal
OL,17,Fimage of a child, which had been
OL,18,Fdownloaded from the internet and was
OL,19,Fin the most serious category.
