OL,6,FAnother phone belonging to Drury was
OL,7,Fseized and found to contain further
OL,8,Findecent images.
OL,10,FHe was charged with multiple offences
OL,11,Fbut denied any wrongdoing and was
OL,12,Fgranted bail by magistrates, pending
OL,13,Ffuture court proceedings.
OL,15,FDrury went on to commit further
OL,16,Foffences and was arrested again, in
OL,17,FAugust 2024, after initiating contact
OL,18,Fwith a person who he believed to be a
OL,19,F14-year-old child.
