OL,6,FIn relation to the online offences, he
OL,7,Fpreviously pleaded guilty to attempted
OL,8,Fsexual communication with a child,
OL,9,Fattempting to cause a child to watch
OL,10,Fothers engaging in sexual activity and
OL,11,Fattempting to incite a child to engage
OL,12,Fin sexual activity.
OL,14,FOn 4 September 2025, Drury, of Borough
OL,15,FGreen Road, Wrotham was sentenced to
OL,16,Ffour years and six months'
OL,17,Fimprisonment.
OL,19,FHe was also made the subject of a
OL,20,FSexual Harm Prevention Order, lasting
OL,21,F15 years.
